Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pathvisio.core.network.Node

  • public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
    Node, the elemental structure used as source/target in an Edge object , can be of type data/ reaction node Data nodes are uniquely identified by their Xref Reaction nodes are uniquely identified by their reaction id
